  "body": "Local storage is not expected to be available as a scheduling resource in v1.7.\r\nKubelet is incorrectly exposing a resource named `storage`.\r\nThis is incorrect because the feature is alpha and so it requires opt-in via feature flags and,\r\nthe resource names are invalid.\r\nThe expected resource names are listed [here](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/api/v1/types.go#L3533) - `storage.kubernetes.io/scratch` and `storage.kubernetes.io/overlay`.\r\n\r\ncc @jingxu97 @saad-ali \r\n\r\nThis is v1.7 blocker because we cannot expose a new resource in the API and rename it in a subsequent release.\r\n\r\n@kubernetes/sig-storage-bugs ",
